The,Snowflake,Widget,API,allows,rd,party,sites,to,display,the,Simply,Wall,St,s,Snowflake,for,any,company,in,the,Simply,Wall,St,database,or,display,another,company,at,random,that,fits,a,specific,criteria,The,Snowflake,is,generated,by,Simply,Wall,St,and,an,associated,infographic,for,companies,on,the,NYSE,Nasdaq,LSE,and,ASX,is,also,generated,daily